                    <h1 class="domdom">29</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1389">Oh! What A Lovely War (1969) </a></h1>

                    <h2>29 Jun 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Oh! What a Lovely War redefines the tragedy of World War 1 in bawdy music-hall terms. Of the many fleeting satiric images 
parading past the camera, one of the most indelible is the sight of 
several generals playing leapfrog as the world all around them goes to 
hell.</p>

